extends _base

block title
  title Loading 

block sidebar
  +sidebar('Loading')

block content

  h2.sui-page-header 开发者文档

  p.sui-lead 使用iconfont+keyframe,IE10以下降级显示为静态的，IE10、11正常

  ul.sui-nav.nav-tabs.nav-large
    li.active
      a(href='#demo1', data-toggle='tab') 示例
    li
      a(href='#code1', data-toggle='tab') 代码
    li
      a(href='#doc1', data-toggle='tab') 文档

  div.tab-content
    div.tab-pane.active#demo1
      div.bs-docs-example
        p .sui-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-dark.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-light.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading

        hr
        p loading-large, loading-xlarge, loading-xxlarge
        div.sui-loading.loading-large
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-xlarge
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-xxlarge
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        hr
        p loading-small, loading-xsmall, loading-xxsmall
        div.sui-loading.loading-small.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-xsmall.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading
        div.sui-loading.loading-xxsmall.loading-inline
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading


        hr
        p loading-dark, .loading-light

        hr

        input(type=text style="vertical-align:top")
        div.sui-loading.loading-xxsmall.loading-inline.loading-light
          i.sui-icon.icon-pc-loading


    div.tab-pane#code1
      pre.prettyprint.linenums(data-target='#demo1>div')
    div.tab-pane#doc1
      p 很简单，可以自己定制尺寸
      p 为方便使用，默认有几种推荐的尺寸,分别对应class:  loading-small,loading-xsmall,loading-xxsmall, loading-l, loading-ll, loading-lll
      p 默认作为块级盒子显示，.sui-loading.loading-inline 则会以内联盒子形式显示 （inline-block）
      p 颜色方面有默认色、黑色、灰色三种, .sui-loading.loading-dark .loading-light 
  ul.demo-operations.clearfix
    li
      a.copy-btn(href='javascript:void(0)', data-target='#demo1>div') 复制代码

